      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"fresh perspective\" thing... i've tried that. therapists, friends, everything. it's just like trying to patch a sink with tape. the water just keeps coming. it feels less like a phase and more like a design flaw. like i was just built to fail and repeat this cycle forever. it's just... heavy. i'm so heavy.",
