      "content": "it's not even about the \"support\" anymore. i'm just so weary of the effort it takes to just exist. it feels like i'm stuck in a loop that's never going to resolve, no matter how much \"structured support\" i get. eventually, you realize that some loops don't have an exit, they just have an end. the only way to actually stop the cycle is to just stop everything.",
